 *   DESCRIPTION: 8-bit multiplier
 *
 *   FUNCTION: Uses modular design principles to implement an 8-bit multiplier.
 *             Each add_shift module is called conditionally to add the multiplicand
 *             shifted left by a specific number of positions to an accumulator based
 *             on a corresponding bit in the multiplier.
 *
 *   CHANGE HISTORY:
 *
 *   DATE         NAME     REASON
 *   ------------ -------- -----------------------------------------------
 *   03/12/97    M.R.     Initial Release
 *
